flowchart TB
    K0[Key: held = empty] --> L1[Lock Level 1]
    L1 --> K1[Key: held = up to 1]
    K1 --> L2[Lock Level 2]
    L2 --> K2[Key: held = up to 2]
    K2 --> L3[Lock Level 3]
    L3 --> K3[Key: held = up to 3]
    K1 -.->|attempt level 1 again| ERR[compile error]
    K2 -.->|attempt level 1| ERR
    style ERR fill:#ffcccc
